spirits categories to include them in the same relevant market, although, as elaborated below we believe that this substitutability occurs within broad price bands.  As we shall indicate, the Commission\'92s arguments for placing the various spirit categories
 in separate relevant markets is plausible only with respect to the highest price band. }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
