\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\f8\lang2057\f4\fs24\f4\lang1025\qj 155.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 We have already dealt with the evidence on substitution between the traditional spirit categories at some length and have concluded that there is sufficient evidence to factor this phenomenon into the definition of the relevant market.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\f8\lang2057\f4\fs24\f4\lang1025\qj 156.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 As for the market segmentation based on price differentials, consider how deeply embedded in the thinking of industry participants is the three-way distinction between \'91value\'92 brands, \'91proprietary\'92 brands and \'91premium\'92 brands.  Most of the witnesses who pa
rticipated at the hearing articulated their marketing strategies and that of their competitors in terms of this approach. }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\chcbpat9\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\f8\lang2057\f4\fs24\f4\lang1025\qj 157.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 While these consumer segments are, by no means, absolutely coterminous with income level (nor, we should note, is the LSM concept conventionally used in market research), there is clearly a close relationship between branding strategy and price simply beca
use income and the related ability to participate in the market is a critical, the most critical, element in the construction of the consumer segment at which a particular brand is targeted.  Certainly, a fundamental marketing strategy is to drive consumer
s up the brand ladder, to persuade them to desert the lower reaches of the market in favour of higher value brands.  But there are limits imposed on this strategy \'96 as the saying goes \'91the poor will always be with us\'92, the rich will always be willing to pa
y a premium for consuming the \'91extrinsic\'92 qualities that identify them as a group distinguishable from the rest of society, and entrepreneurs will constantly strive to segment their markets.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\f8\lang2057\f4\fs24\f4\lang1025\qj 158.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 The occasions on which the distinction between the value, proprietary and premium categories informed the various analyses presented to us by all the witnesses are too numerous to list.  Seagrams and DGB presented us with a detailed map locating the variou
s spirit brands in the three segments of value, proprietary and premium.  Snell\'92s competitive advantage (and, we are told, its Achilles heel) manifests the existence and significance of this market segmentation most starkly.  Snell is the dominant producer
 and distributor of \'91value\'92 brands, those brands serving the bottom end of the market.  It has developed highly successful brandy, whisky and white spirits brands.  But it is struggling to transform one or more of its brands from the low margin value segme
nt to the higher margin proprietary segment.  In recent years it has been anchored to the value segment by Distell\'92s efforts to penetrate that segment.  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
