e brand \'96 Snell is simultaneously taking on the likes of Distell and GUDV in the proprietary sector, while, through migrating a successful value brand, it eases the ability of these formidable competitors to penetrate the value segment.  Indeed, this predi
cament, which we re-examine below, appears to be the basis of Snell\'92s objection to the transaction.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
