ily substitute between different spirit types and, further research may well reveal, may even substitute between spirits and, because of this country\'92s unusually large market for inexpensive wine, wine.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
