stell\'92s market shares in each of the relevant markets under scrutiny is, on the face of it, cause for concern, this is somewhat ameliorated by an examination of the relatively small additions to market share achieved in consequence of the merger. }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
