nd hence required notification and evaluation, it remains nevertheless that their identical ownership structures undoubtedly compromised the intensity of pre-merger competition between the parties.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
