ue and premium markets there is not a substantial lessening of competition, in the proprietary market, on the other hand, competition is compromised by the transaction.  We will examine each of these in turn.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang2057\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057 
