cerns regarding the impact on competition, this factor serves to exacerbate our concerns.  Distell enjoys a very powerful position in the FABs market - a market share of 70.8% in 2000 and 61.8% in 2001.  Had we elected to include FABs in the relevant marke
t, Distell\'92s market share would have been considerably larger, rising, we estimate, to 51,8% of the prop spirits and FABs market.}
